title: Harry Styles’ new film is a mess. But it gets this right.

media:group.media:title: Harry Styles’ new film is a mess. But it gets this right.
media:group.media:description:
Harry Styles’ new film “Don’t Worry Darling” has a surprisingly liberty-oriented message… In a 1950s community where wives have abundant material possessions, something is still lacking: autonomy. Freedom from coercion and the ability to pursue what’s individually meaningful transcends political affiliations and should motivate us all.
